longBusinessSummary: Entheon Biomedical Corp., a biotechnology research and drug development company, engages in developing and commercializing various N,N-dimethyltryptamine based psychedelic therapeutic products for treating addiction and substance use disorders. The company is headquartered in Coquitlam, Canada.
